WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:02.027
Hey, good morning family.

00:00:02.027 --> 00:00:03.246
Praise the Lord.

00:00:03.246 --> 00:00:04.960
Thank you for joining me today.

00:00:04.960 --> 00:00:08.192
Well, Diana's behind the camera today, and I have a word for you.

00:00:08.192 --> 00:00:11.342
So, I'm going to tell you all some things that have been on my heart.

00:00:11.617 --> 00:00:13.319
I got my Amazon order in.

00:00:13.319 --> 00:00:15.120
I love to feed my squirrels.

00:00:16.220 --> 00:00:18.120
I love to feed squirrels and I love to watch them.

00:00:18.120 --> 00:00:22.297
I told Diana, I said, "I'm going to go out and get the squirrels' food all around.

00:00:22.560 --> 00:00:25.230
" I was putting it all inside the feeders.

00:00:25.230 --> 00:00:30.419
And the Lord spoke to me and he said to me, "Brandon, you like to watch the squirrels.

00:00:30.419 --> 00:00:33.316
" And he said, "I like to watch you.

00:00:33.316 --> 00:00:35.342
I like to watch my kids.

00:00:35.342 --> 00:00:37.792
I like to bless my kids.

00:00:37.792 --> 00:00:41.966
" And he said, "Brandon, the squirrels didn't earn the food.

00:00:41.966 --> 00:00:43.860
They didn't deserve the food.

00:00:43.860 --> 00:00:47.789
" He said, "It was grace that you did this today for them.

00:00:47.789 --> 00:00:56.034
" And he said, "What's about to happen in these last days is going to be my grace poured out on the people with finances.

00:00:56.034 --> 00:01:04.749
" And he goes, "It will be to people that you don't feel in your heart when I tell you to give to somebody a big money.

00:01:05.199 --> 00:01:07.520
They don't treat you right.

00:01:07.520 --> 00:01:12.050
They didn't act like they like you, but it wasn't about you.

00:01:12.050 --> 00:01:14.915
It was about me just blessing them through you.

00:01:14.915 --> 00:01:23.840
As long as you can keep your eyes focused on me and attract to deflect, I'll work through you.

00:01:24.920 --> 00:01:32.880
" He said to me, "It's not always that they deserve it, and it's not always that they earned it.

00:01:32.880 --> 00:01:34.080
It's just grace.

00:01:34.080 --> 00:01:40.639
And it's not because they treated you right or they treated you wrong.

00:01:40.639 --> 00:01:46.913
" He said, "You give secretly and I'll reward you openly.

00:01:46.913 --> 00:01:58.880
The bigger the checks I tell you to give, the more it is to die to self because I will not share my glory with anyone.

00:01:58.880 --> 00:02:09.240
It's always when you lay hands on somebody in the days ahead and they get healed from cancer or diabetes, and instantaneously they're like, 'You're my new best friend,' right?

00:02:16.319 --> 00:02:24.249
Because you laid hands on them and it solved a problem that was killing them, but it had nothing to do with you.

00:02:24.249 --> 00:02:29.413
You are just the person that God used to distribute the glory, right?

00:02:29.413 --> 00:02:35.139
The anointing of his presence destroys the yoke, but it has nothing to do with you.

00:02:35.139 --> 00:02:36.340
You're just a vessel.

00:02:36.340 --> 00:02:39.200
So, it's the same way about the finances.

00:02:39.200 --> 00:02:50.149
The Lord said to me, 'I'll not share my glory with anyone concerning healing, and I'll not share at this level of where I'm taking certain people with finances.

00:02:50.149 --> 00:02:59.222
' And he said, 'One percent, Brandon, one percent will walk in this end-time wealth of this kind of wealth that I'm talking about.

00:02:59.222 --> 00:03:05.840
' And I've brought that up before to you all and told you about the one percent.

00:03:05.840 --> 00:03:12.919
But I'm talking about extreme wealth, extreme wealth, like more than deca-millionaires.

00:03:16.500 --> 00:03:20.027
I'm not talking about you got a couple hundred thousand dollars in the bank and you're going, 'Well, you know, I'm able to have extra in my...

00:03:20.027 --> 00:03:22.020
' That's not extreme wealth.

00:03:22.020 --> 00:03:28.871
That's not like lavish, like where you go, 'Wow,' to the world's standards when the world's looking at you and going, 'What is going on?

00:03:28.871 --> 00:03:31.560
How—what are they got going on with them?

00:03:31.560 --> 00:03:35.120
' It's all about Jesus, you know what I'm saying?

00:03:44.020 --> 00:03:44.370
You attract to deflect, and this is what it will be with finances.

00:03:50.299 --> 00:03:55.531
And he told me it will be as precise as listening to him as a clock ticks to listen for when he tells you to invest in something.

00:03:55.531 --> 00:04:09.706
When I talked about the pillars, listening to what those pillars are and when to invest in those pillars and listening to him and saying, 'Father, not my will, but yours be done.

00:04:09.706 --> 00:04:13.689
' But it's all about being like—I want to call it a secret assassin.

00:04:18.834 --> 00:04:19.142
You're mysterious.

00:04:20.070 --> 00:04:21.938
You walk in and you do the job.

00:04:28.240 --> 00:04:28.600
You do the mission for the government of the Lord.

00:04:28.600 --> 00:04:31.067
You want to say it's cool.

00:04:36.251 --> 00:04:36.479
In the government of the Lord, you are an ambassador of the Lord.

00:04:36.479 --> 00:04:37.546
You work for him.

00:04:37.546 --> 00:04:39.759
You're doing exactly what he's told you to do.

00:04:39.759 --> 00:04:41.104
You're his hands.

00:04:41.104 --> 00:04:42.370
You're his feet.

00:04:42.370 --> 00:04:43.299
You're maneuvering.

00:04:43.299 --> 00:04:49.600
You're moving in that circumstance, and you drop it and you get out, and it's all about him.

00:04:49.600 --> 00:04:52.686
So they're wondering what happened, what in the world went on.

00:04:54.377 --> 00:04:57.406
The glory came and we don't even know what happened.

00:04:57.406 --> 00:04:59.839
It changed the whole atmosphere.

00:05:06.280 --> 00:05:10.880
The healing power of God came in.

00:05:10.880 --> 00:05:15.440
He said, 'Be made whole,' like I was talking about spirit, soul, and body—the whole man.

00:05:15.440 --> 00:05:16.880
It's not just about healing.

00:05:16.880 --> 00:05:21.510
He said, 'I'm going to use people for healings and to restore back what the cankerworm ate.

00:05:21.510 --> 00:05:25.840
But I'm not going to share my glory with anyone, Brandon, in these last days.

00:05:26.249 --> 00:05:28.830
And if you can work with me like that, we'll work great together.

00:05:28.830 --> 00:05:35.520
' Just like the squirrels, they don't even know when the food's coming, but I pour the food in there and I just like to watch them.

00:05:35.520 --> 00:05:36.480
They're so excited.

00:05:36.480 --> 00:05:40.200
They run down the tree and they're eating and they're filling their mouths full.

00:05:40.200 --> 00:05:44.114
They don't even realize that there was just grace that just happened.

00:05:44.114 --> 00:05:48.040
It was a grace explosion that all that food was in that little feeder.

00:05:49.530 --> 00:05:50.530
And they're going, 'Man, this is so good.

00:05:50.530 --> 00:05:58.309
' And they take it and they run off, and they don't go and say, 'Thank you, sir,' you know, waving from the branch.

00:06:00.194 --> 00:06:01.120
They just go, 'Man, I just had a really good day.

00:06:01.120 --> 00:06:04.100
I don't know where all that came from, but it blessed my day.

00:06:04.100 --> 00:06:07.371
' And watching that blessing blesses me.

00:06:11.143 --> 00:06:11.440
And that's what he said.

00:06:11.440 --> 00:06:13.600
That's where he's at.

00:06:13.600 --> 00:06:16.400
He just wants to see his kids happy.

00:06:16.400 --> 00:06:23.840
He just wants to see his kids happy and he's just loving on them.

00:06:27.639 --> 00:06:28.911
And sometimes you just take and you put some cash in somebody's hand or whatever.

00:06:28.911 --> 00:06:30.096
Holy Ghost handshakes.

00:06:30.096 --> 00:06:32.057
'How are you doing, brother?

00:06:32.057 --> 00:06:34.900
God bless you,' and just walk away.

00:06:35.500 --> 00:06:40.160
And they don't even realize that you gave maybe a couple hundred bucks or something.

00:06:44.380 --> 00:06:44.590
You know what I'm saying?

00:06:50.308 --> 00:06:50.696
And you just flow that way.

00:06:50.696 --> 00:07:02.834
But the Lord was talking about how whenever it comes down to healings and demonstrations and the manifestations of the glory, who is going to be the elites of walking with him will always be to attract the glory.

00:07:10.640 --> 00:07:10.879
The presence of the Lord brings the people to you, and then you push them to him.

00:07:10.879 --> 00:07:15.840
So I see the squirrels as how they're a blessing to me.

00:07:23.640 --> 00:07:23.900
And I know that we are not squirrels; we're his kids.

00:07:23.900 --> 00:07:35.460
But he was using it as something to instruct me that day, is that he said, 'Brandon, I just want you to know there'll be one percent that flows in this end-time wealth transfer of the great wealth.

00:07:44.570 --> 00:07:44.880
And I'll not share my glory, just like I won't share my glory whenever you pray for somebody and they try to say, "Thank you, sir.

00:07:44.880 --> 00:07:46.251
" No, it ain't you.

00:07:46.251 --> 00:07:47.383
I'm just a vessel.

00:07:47.383 --> 00:07:52.920
We got to always keep the main thing the main thing and give God praise for everything in these last days.

00:07:52.920 --> 00:08:01.144
We have to always be looking at his face and knowing that he is the rewarder of those that diligently seek him, not Brandon.

00:08:01.144 --> 00:08:02.834
I may write a check.

00:08:02.834 --> 00:08:07.520
I may be the distributor of the wealth that he gave me, but it's always to give God the praise.

00:08:08.293 --> 00:08:09.840
And it will be for the unlikely people.

00:08:09.840 --> 00:08:11.379
They may not treat you right.

00:08:25.223 --> 00:08:25.509
You say, "I don't think they treat me very good.

00:08:31.546 --> 00:08:31.840
I don't think they're very kind to me.

00:08:32.426 --> 00:08:35.072
" And that's usually probably the ones that he wants to bless the most.

00:08:37.120 --> 00:08:55.488
That's why I thought it was interesting about the healings, because he was talking about you'll see healings on people that are strung out on drugs, strung out, and they're not the ones that are believing and going over there in the corner having all the Bible verses like sister so-and-so, and she's all—and she may be struggling with something.

00:08:55.488 --> 00:08:57.051
She might die by something.

00:08:57.051 --> 00:08:58.240
I don't know.

00:09:06.810 --> 00:09:07.020
It's not my job to test the hearts.

00:09:12.399 --> 00:09:12.679
All I do is obey.

00:09:13.599 --> 00:09:20.010
And you go and he'll say, "Pray for that lady right there on the side of the road," and she could be a hooker.

00:09:22.480 --> 00:09:26.537
And the power of God hits her and you go, "My God, she had a creative miracle!

00:09:26.537 --> 00:09:32.640
" And it was just something she didn't earn and something she didn't deserve.

00:09:32.640 --> 00:09:35.519
It's called grace.

00:09:42.720 --> 00:09:42.940
And that's exactly who He is, a God of grace, and He is a God of love.

00:09:51.519 --> 00:09:51.732
And you didn't earn salvation and you didn't deserve salvation, but it's just His grace.

00:09:57.531 --> 00:09:58.880
And He said, 'I love you and I've provided a way for you that you don't have to go to hell today.

00:09:58.880 --> 00:10:05.040
' I'm trying to tell you that's what He's talking about: the end-time wealth transfer of what's about to happen with the finances.

00:10:05.040 --> 00:10:12.526
It's something you can't earn and it's something you don't deserve, but God said, 'I'm going to bless you.

00:10:12.526 --> 00:10:16.213
' And I've seen what's about to happen again with a glimpse.

00:10:16.213 --> 00:10:29.383
As I was lying in bed, I could see over and I was looking into these months ahead of what God is trying to do just for His remnant, for the people who He just wants to watch and see.

00:10:29.383 --> 00:10:42.800
It's like when you go on Christmas morning and you've given your kids all these beautiful presents and you're excited just to see their expression of the package that you've wrapped up in a bow, and they're going to go, 'Daddy, look at what you got me today!

00:10:42.800 --> 00:10:47.463
' and they're so excited and celebrating that present that they got.

00:10:59.680 --> 00:10:59.886
And that's what He's looking at, as a good daddy, for healings and blessings.

00:10:59.886 --> 00:11:02.320
And He's going, 'I know, I just love my kids.

00:11:02.320 --> 00:11:04.080
' You know what I'm saying?

00:11:04.080 --> 00:11:07.700
When you love your kids, you just do good things for them.

00:11:15.080 --> 00:11:15.440
And that's why it even goes to Scripture.

00:11:15.440 --> 00:11:25.509
It says, 'If we, being evil, give good gifts to our kids, how much more does our heavenly Father give good gifts to those that love Him?

00:11:25.509 --> 00:11:30.133
' And I just know that my Daddy's a good daddy.

00:11:30.133 --> 00:11:35.013
He's a God that rewards those that diligently seek Him today.

00:11:35.013 --> 00:11:53.839
And I thought, as I watch my squirrels—I don't want to be a squirrel, but I want to be a kid that is just innocently seeking Him and being hungry after even the corn, saying, 'Man, I'm just so thankful that He blessed me today.

00:11:53.839 --> 00:12:07.210
' So if He asks you to give a check to somebody or asks you to pray for somebody that you don't feel like deserves it, it's just God saying, 'I just want to give them a hug today.

00:12:07.210 --> 00:12:12.906
' It's something they didn't earn and it's something they didn't deserve.

00:12:12.906 --> 00:12:34.346
But sometimes He may ask you to do something that's uncomfortable to your flesh, and you think, 'Well, I'd like to give it to the lady that's over here that's been praying a lot or whatever,' but He's just wanting to love on the unlovelies.

00:12:40.469 --> 00:12:40.754
And they may have a cranky attitude; they may have a demeanor that's just a bad attitude or whatever.

00:12:45.600 --> 00:12:45.973
And you may think, 'Well, they don't deserve this.

00:12:45.973 --> 00:12:48.159
' But that's just God's grace explosion.

00:12:48.159 --> 00:12:49.929
That's God's grace explosion.

00:12:49.929 --> 00:12:54.420
He's just wanting to show that He's a good God.

00:12:54.420 --> 00:12:58.463
And I'm telling you, that's what's about to happen.

00:12:58.463 --> 00:13:07.870
So, this is just the last part of this little thing I have for y'all.

00:13:21.531 --> 00:13:21.782
I keep seeing the people moving from major city areas to come to the country.

00:13:34.293 --> 00:13:34.587
I keep seeing this virus.

00:13:35.232 --> 00:13:35.935
I keep seeing great shaking, y'all.

00:13:44.740 --> 00:13:45.150
And it doesn't let up.

00:13:45.150 --> 00:13:50.079
I keep seeing waves of it.

00:13:50.079 --> 00:13:57.570
Praying as we saw the shooter on the military base yesterday and so many people got injured, folks.

00:13:57.570 --> 00:14:00.240
We're living in the last of the last days here.

00:14:00.240 --> 00:14:03.653
There'll be major decisions being made even concerning Judge Torres.

00:14:14.418 --> 00:14:14.667
And I told you I saw three new trillionaires.

00:14:14.667 --> 00:14:16.304
This is—I've never seen this before.

00:14:16.304 --> 00:14:17.456
There's usually hundred-billionaires or whatever, big money.

00:14:17.456 --> 00:14:19.199
But I'm telling you, I saw trillionaires coming.

00:14:19.199 --> 00:14:22.172
Now, will they be—will that be the only three trillionaires in the world?

00:14:22.172 --> 00:14:23.172
Heavens, no!

00:14:23.172 --> 00:14:28.160
But it's what the Lord is showing me and what these men represent.

00:14:28.160 --> 00:14:30.800
I told you all it was a Saudi Arabian prince.

00:14:32.160 --> 00:14:33.519
It is not a Saudi Arabian prince.

00:14:33.519 --> 00:14:37.874
My son said it is the United Arab Emirates.

00:14:46.862 --> 00:14:47.173
I might have butchered that, but I'm trying.

00:14:47.173 --> 00:14:56.460
But that man, I saw a man that is a trillionaire and he's heavily invested in a certain thing.

00:14:56.460 --> 00:14:58.994
Then Michael Saylor, and I saw BlackRock—those three things.

00:14:58.994 --> 00:14:59.451
Okay.

00:14:59.451 --> 00:15:04.100
So I saw in those three things three new trillion-dollar things that are about to take place.

00:15:12.639 --> 00:15:13.599
And I thought that was interesting because I know there's other people that have invested in certain things, but the Lord showed me these three people.

00:15:25.611 --> 00:15:25.989
And I don't know why, but there's a reason.

00:15:28.275 --> 00:15:28.737
The Lord doesn't talk just to hear Himself talk.

00:15:28.737 --> 00:15:34.835
Ladies and gentlemen, He speaks to make real things happen in the real world.

00:15:44.319 --> 00:15:44.613
And I'm telling you, God is going to show you things for a strategic purpose.

00:15:44.613 --> 00:15:53.269
When it comes to—I said I saw the 76ers, the Philadelphia Eagles, I saw the New York Jets, I saw people not going to major stadiums in the days ahead.

00:15:53.269 --> 00:15:55.770
Those are all in the same area.

00:16:01.160 --> 00:16:01.410
You would think, 'Well, how would they go bankrupt, Brandon?

00:16:01.410 --> 00:16:04.631
' I'm telling you, there was something that happened.

00:16:17.440 --> 00:16:17.780
And then I freaked everybody out about the trees, the bushes with the berries for coffee.

00:16:17.780 --> 00:16:20.514
Now, what causes the coffee bean shortage?

00:16:20.514 --> 00:16:21.439
Something happens.

00:16:21.439 --> 00:16:38.489
It's either something happens with the trees, like a pest, because I don't want to add to or take away from anything, but I'm telling you, when I saw the coffee bean shortage, it was a major something happening with these trees, and I saw fires.

00:16:38.489 --> 00:16:45.106
I saw environmental issues coming with the shortage, with drought and things to do with coffee beans.

00:16:56.839 --> 00:16:57.960
And I was like, 'That's interesting,' because I was driving by a Starbucks and I saw the vision of a shortage in Starbucks, and they were shutting down stores because there was a problem with the beans.

00:16:58.920 --> 00:17:00.120
How often does a coffee bean bush produce coffee beans?

00:17:11.085 --> 00:17:11.370
I have no idea.

00:17:16.223 --> 00:17:16.367
I'm not an expert in coffee.

00:17:19.831 --> 00:17:21.217
I just come on here and people are like, 'Oh my God, I've got to go buy a bunch of coffee!

00:17:21.217 --> 00:17:24.390
' And I'm like, 'No, that's not what I said.

00:17:24.390 --> 00:17:30.930
' I said, 'I just thought it was interesting because the Lord shows me these glimpses when I'm driving around praying about the babies and the incubators.

00:17:30.930 --> 00:17:34.940
' And the things that I saw this last time, some of this stuff was very dark.

00:17:34.940 --> 00:17:36.999
It was creepy—the surrogate baby machines.

00:17:48.146 --> 00:17:48.373
It was really weird.

00:17:48.373 --> 00:17:53.720
So then somebody sends me a video and says, 'Brandon, you're seeing right on this, dude.

00:17:53.720 --> 00:17:59.947
The dude that's trying to create one of the chips for the brain is creating the baby machine.

00:17:59.947 --> 00:18:07.280
' And I was like—I told Dian, I go—and the Lord said, 'This will happen in the not-too-distant future.

00:18:07.280 --> 00:18:10.639
Some of these things you will see will happen in the not-too-distant future.

00:18:10.639 --> 00:18:20.512
' And I'm going to say this: they say, 'Well, should I take the cure for cancer or the cure for diabetes if it comes out?

00:18:20.512 --> 00:18:21.535
' Heavens, yes!

00:18:21.535 --> 00:18:22.807
Why would you not?

00:18:26.840 --> 00:18:31.680
If you're suffering with something, you're dying of something and they have it through AI to fix it, fix it.

00:18:31.680 --> 00:18:50.880
If it's not a mark in your hand or in your forehead, or you're saying allegiance to some kind of entity saying, 'Oh, I bow my knee to you' like Shadrach, Meshach, and Abednego, or any of Daniel or the lion's den or whatever, of course, take it.

00:18:53.920 --> 00:18:59.880
I'm not saying an allegiance to the devil, but if I get a cure through medical science, it's a blessing.

00:18:59.880 --> 00:19:17.600
It's like saying I don't want to go to medical science if they have a cure for some kind of something, and I don't want to get a shot or whatever I need to do to fix that if they have the means to help you with it.

00:19:20.960 --> 00:19:21.920
I feel like this is part of the solution to help people of what's coming.

00:19:21.920 --> 00:19:24.120
But it's a bait and a hook.

00:19:24.120 --> 00:19:29.280
They're trying to hook you to get you desensitized to the beast system that's coming.

00:19:38.220 --> 00:19:38.720
Do you reject it?

00:19:43.920 --> 00:19:46.788
I said you harness it.

00:19:56.799 --> 00:19:56.986
You don't embrace it like a friend; you harness it like a tool.

00:19:56.986 --> 00:19:57.920
Does that make sense?

00:19:57.920 --> 00:19:59.965
You don't embrace it; you harness it.

00:20:01.520 --> 00:20:01.760
And you wield it.

00:20:01.760 --> 00:20:06.669
You're like you're cutting with the saw or whatever.

00:20:06.669 --> 00:20:11.200
There'll be things in it that'll be a blessing to you in the days ahead.

00:20:11.200 --> 00:20:14.160
But ultimately, it will all lead to destruction.

00:20:27.280 --> 00:20:27.640
All of it will.

00:20:36.320 --> 00:20:36.640
And all we have to do is ride the wave until Jesus comes.

00:20:43.028 --> 00:20:47.490
And know that you don't let it all in your house and let it start teaching your kids spiritual things or whatever, or asking it counsel or advice about whatever, but you just know it's a surface thing.

00:20:58.632 --> 00:20:58.848
You touch it like it's hot, and that's hot.

00:20:58.848 --> 00:21:15.556
Well, I gotta, you know, I don't know how else to describe it to y'all because there's so many people that will have the cure for something that you're overcoming and you'll die, and the Lord's trying to help you.

00:21:15.556 --> 00:21:18.176
Well, God is always going to use something else.

00:21:18.176 --> 00:21:19.424
I don't know, God's sovereign.

00:21:19.424 --> 00:21:21.579
He'll use whatever He wants to use.

00:21:28.320 --> 00:21:30.720
But I'm not going to put Him in a box and say, "God, you have to do exactly what I want you to do because this is what makes me feel comfortable.

00:21:30.720 --> 00:21:31.232
